## Contributing

When adding new features:
1. Create a test script following this guide
2. Add corresponding API tests to `test_api.sh` if needed
3. Add corresponding page tests to `test_pages.sh` if needed
4. Ensure tests align with audit requirements
5. Update this README with new test coverage
6. Verify tests are idempotent and independent

